refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public static stringSeasLog::getDatetimeFormat
Obtém o formato de data/horário do SeasLog. Use o método SeasLog::getDatetimeFormat para obter o valor de seaslog.default_datetime_format configurado no php.ini (ou seaslog.ini).

  &reftitle.examples;

   Exemplo de SeasLog::getDatetimeFormat


<?php

var_dump(SeasLog::getDateTimeFormat());
var_dump(SeasLog::setDateTimeFormat('Ymd His'));
var_dump(SeasLog::getDateTimeFormat());

?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


string(11) "Y-m-d H:i:s"
bool(true)
string(7) "Ymd His"
